WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.550
Hey, good morning family. How are you

00:00:02.550 --> 00:00:02.560
all

00:00:02.560 --> 00:00:05.510
doing today? I have my wife

00:00:05.520 --> 00:00:09.030
with me again, my companion, my friend.

00:00:09.040 --> 00:00:10.390
We're excited. We're going to talk to you

00:00:10.390 --> 00:00:10.400
all

00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:12.629
about hearing the voice of

00:00:12.639 --> 00:00:15.589
the Lord and following the peace of God

00:00:15.599 --> 00:00:18.710
in your life so that you can hear

00:00:18.720 --> 00:00:21.750
Him for yourself. The Holy Spirit

00:00:21.760 --> 00:00:23.750
is no respecter of persons. The Lord is

00:00:23.760 --> 00:00:26.310
not. And I believe with all my heart

00:00:26.320 --> 00:00:29.189
that He wants you to live a good

00:00:29.199 --> 00:00:31.589
life, to live a life full of

00:00:31.599 --> 00:00:33.990
abundance to the full until it overflows.

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:36.069
We don't have to struggle

00:00:36.079 --> 00:00:38.790
spiritually, physically, financially,

00:00:38.800 --> 00:00:41.430
mentally, or emotionally in any area of our

00:00:41.440 --> 00:00:43.990
life. He wants us to be successful.

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:46.229
You know, we get a lot of people

00:00:46.239 --> 00:00:49.270
emailing us on a day-to-day basis

00:00:49.280 --> 00:00:51.350
asking, 'Hey, can you hear the Lord for

00:00:51.360 --> 00:00:53.350
me? Can you tell me where I'm supposed

00:00:53.360 --> 00:00:56.069
to invest my money? Can you tell me if

00:00:56.079 --> 00:00:58.470
I'm supposed to move or if I'm supposed

00:00:58.480 --> 00:01:01.110
to buy a new

00:01:01.110 --> 00:01:01.120
car?'It's

00:01:01.120 --> 00:01:03.270
amazing the emails that we

00:01:03.280 --> 00:01:06.630
get. I see the lack in

00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:08.390
the body of Christ of hearing the voice

00:01:08.400 --> 00:01:11.270
of God for themselves. The prophets

00:01:11.270 --> 00:01:11.280
of

00:01:11.280 --> 00:01:14.310
old, they heard for the

00:01:14.320 --> 00:01:17.670
world. They heard what was coming

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:19.830
because the Holy Spirit didn't dwell

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:23.030
in each individual person yet,

00:01:23.030 --> 00:01:23.040
since

00:01:23.040 --> 00:01:25.749
Jesus hadn't died on the cross.

00:01:25.749 --> 00:01:25.759
When

00:01:25.759 --> 00:01:28.310
He died on the cross, He came

00:01:28.320 --> 00:01:30.630
and He lives on the inside of every

00:01:30.640 --> 00:01:33.990
believer. The moment you receive Jesus

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:37.030
Christ as your Lord and Savior, you have

00:01:37.040 --> 00:01:39.109
your wall-to-wall Holy Ghost.

00:01:39.119 --> 00:01:41.270
He dwells on the inside of you.

00:01:41.280 --> 00:01:42.390
It's exciting

00:01:42.400 --> 00:01:45.109
as a believer. That's right.

00:01:45.119 --> 00:01:47.510
And

00:01:47.520 --> 00:01:50.149
it's for a child too. The

00:01:50.149 --> 00:01:50.159
moment

00:01:50.159 --> 00:01:53.429
a child

00:01:53.429 --> 00:01:53.439
asks

00:01:53.439 --> 00:01:56.230
Jesus Christ to be the Lord and Savior,

00:01:56.240 --> 00:01:58.310
they have the ability to hear the Lord.

00:01:58.320 --> 00:02:00.469
He didn't make it hard;

00:02:00.479 --> 00:02:01.749
we make it hard

00:02:02.159 --> 00:02:04.789
by trying to complicate it with our

00:02:04.799 --> 00:02:06.630
thoughts. I don't know;

00:02:06.640 --> 00:02:09.190
maybe I've developed a different

00:02:09.200 --> 00:02:11.029
kind of relationship with the Lord. It

00:02:11.039 --> 00:02:12.710
seems like in my life, because I've had

00:02:12.720 --> 00:02:15.750
so many challenges with my

00:02:15.760 --> 00:02:17.910
learning, I believe

00:02:17.920 --> 00:02:19.830
maybe there's a lot of simplicity

00:02:19.840 --> 00:02:21.589
in that. It's because I always stick

00:02:21.599 --> 00:02:23.670
with being like a child

00:02:23.680 --> 00:02:25.830
because in my mind, having

00:02:25.840 --> 00:02:27.670
learning disabilities and

00:02:27.680 --> 00:02:29.270
all the

00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:31.190
things that I've gone through in life,

00:02:31.200 --> 00:02:34.630
I've had to trust Him. I've had to get

00:02:34.640 --> 00:02:37.030
down inside every single day and

00:02:37.040 --> 00:02:39.350
say, 'Lord, help me,'because of the

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:41.110
things that I've

00:02:41.110 --> 00:02:41.120
overcome.

00:02:41.120 --> 00:02:44.550
Maybe if you have a genius IQ,

00:02:44.560 --> 00:02:46.790
you try to rely on your more

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:48.550
intellectual self all the time to get

00:02:48.560 --> 00:02:50.309
through life. You feel you don't have to

00:02:50.319 --> 00:02:52.309
have the Holy Spirit.

00:02:53.280 --> 00:02:55.350
I think that intellect can

00:02:55.360 --> 00:02:58.470
sometimes get in the way of

00:02:58.480 --> 00:02:59.750
your relationship with God because if

00:02:59.760 --> 00:03:01.509
you overthink things, it's supposed to

00:03:01.519 --> 00:03:03.589
be very simple and very childlike.

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:07.270
You just come to Him and say, 'God,

00:03:07.280 --> 00:03:09.830
I need you.

00:03:09.840 --> 00:03:11.830
I want to sit at your

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:13.350
feet today;

00:03:13.360 --> 00:03:15.430
tell me what's on

00:03:15.440 --> 00:03:17.670
your heart. Lead me and guide me

00:03:17.670 --> 00:03:17.680
today.'Every

00:03:17.680 --> 00:03:20.470
day you wake up and say,

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:23.750
'Father, I come to you today and I

00:03:23.760 --> 00:03:25.190
thank you that you lead and guide me in

00:03:25.200 --> 00:03:26.949
everything I do

00:03:26.959 --> 00:03:30.309
and every step I take, that it's all of

00:03:30.319 --> 00:03:31.830
you and none of

00:03:31.840 --> 00:03:33.110
me.'Sometimes

00:03:33.120 --> 00:03:35.030
we

00:03:35.040 --> 00:03:35.990
overcomplicate

00:03:36.000 --> 00:03:36.630
it.

00:03:36.640 --> 00:03:37.990
I believe a lot of people

00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:39.830
think that you have to have a

00:03:39.840 --> 00:03:42.869
certain method; it has to be like

00:03:42.879 --> 00:03:44.869
algebra, and it's not.

00:03:47.920 --> 00:03:50.070
A lot of believers

00:03:50.080 --> 00:03:51.270
always ask, 'What's the difference

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:53.350
between my thoughts and the Holy

00:03:53.350 --> 00:03:53.360
Spirit?'They

00:03:53.360 --> 00:03:54.789
ask that all the time. 'How do

00:03:54.799 --> 00:03:56.550
I know it's the Holy Spirit speaking to

00:03:56.550 --> 00:03:56.560
me?'He

00:03:56.560 --> 00:03:59.750
is the one that

00:03:59.760 --> 00:04:01.270
has the peace that passes all

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:02.550
understanding.

00:04:02.560 --> 00:04:05.509
It's that inward peace. If

00:04:05.519 --> 00:04:08.149
you follow your peace...

00:04:08.159 --> 00:04:10.229
I was talking to you all a couple of

00:04:10.239 --> 00:04:13.110
videos ago about how when I talk to somebody

00:04:13.120 --> 00:04:16.229
on the phone or I'm around somebody,

00:04:16.239 --> 00:04:18.229
the Holy Spirit instantaneously tugs

00:04:18.239 --> 00:04:20.870
at my heart. I do not hear an audible

00:04:20.880 --> 00:04:22.390
voice like I'm talking to my wife right

00:04:22.400 --> 00:04:23.670
now.

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:25.590
The Holy

00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:26.790
Spirit doesn't speak like that. He

00:04:26.800 --> 00:04:28.550
speaks in that still, small voice, and I

00:04:28.560 --> 00:04:31.270
follow that peace. If he says

00:04:31.280 --> 00:04:33.110
in my spirit that person

00:04:33.120 --> 00:04:35.670
right there has ill intentions for

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:38.629
you, he automatically speaks inside

00:04:38.639 --> 00:04:42.230
of me to warn me. Or say

00:04:42.230 --> 00:04:42.240
I

00:04:42.240 --> 00:04:44.629
want to

00:04:44.639 --> 00:04:48.150
go and buy a

00:04:48.150 --> 00:04:48.160
mega-house.

00:04:48.160 --> 00:04:50.870
You think, 'Well, God supplies

00:04:50.880 --> 00:04:52.230
all my needs according to His riches

00:04:52.230 --> 00:04:52.240
in

00:04:52.240 --> 00:04:54.790
glory by Christ Jesus, and

00:04:54.800 --> 00:04:56.950
God's just going to provide for us and

00:04:56.960 --> 00:04:58.310
we're just going to go out and buy a

00:04:58.310 --> 00:04:58.320
million-dollar

00:04:58.320 --> 00:05:00.710
house

00:05:00.710 --> 00:05:00.720
today.'That

00:05:00.720 --> 00:05:03.270
could be presumptuous.

00:05:03.280 --> 00:05:05.590
You can get real fleshy and weird by

00:05:05.600 --> 00:05:07.110
trying to follow the peace and

00:05:07.110 --> 00:05:07.120
thinking,

00:05:07.120 --> 00:05:08.469
'Well, I can afford it because

00:05:08.479 --> 00:05:10.390
God's going to provide for

00:05:10.390 --> 00:05:10.400
me,'but

00:05:10.400 --> 00:05:12.150
you have that inward tug saying, 'Don't

00:05:12.160 --> 00:05:14.710
do that. That's foolish. Don't do

00:05:14.710 --> 00:05:14.720
that.'That's

00:05:14.720 --> 00:05:16.710
the Holy Spirit trying to

00:05:16.720 --> 00:05:18.870
lead you and guide you. In the

00:05:18.880 --> 00:05:21.590
natural, you can believe God for more,

00:05:21.600 --> 00:05:23.270
but you need to stay where your faith

00:05:23.270 --> 00:05:23.280
is

00:05:23.280 --> 00:05:25.029
at. If you can't

00:05:25.039 --> 00:05:27.749
believe God for five dollars, how do you

00:05:27.759 --> 00:05:29.110
think you're going to believe God for a

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:31.189
million? You've got to learn how to take

00:05:31.199 --> 00:05:33.430
your baby steps by faith every single

00:05:33.440 --> 00:05:36.230
day and grow it like you go to

00:05:36.240 --> 00:05:38.629
the gym. You work out and

00:05:38.639 --> 00:05:40.790
you're lifting weights, and you

00:05:40.800 --> 00:05:43.510
increase that weight every

00:05:43.520 --> 00:05:45.590
couple of months.

00:05:45.600 --> 00:05:48.070
You get stronger

00:05:48.080 --> 00:05:50.310
and stronger.

00:05:50.320 --> 00:05:52.390
Eventually, you're going to be able to

00:05:52.400 --> 00:05:54.230
lift a lot more than what you did

00:05:54.240 --> 00:05:56.550
when you first started.

00:05:56.560 --> 00:05:58.230
But you've got to take it a

00:05:58.240 --> 00:06:00.070
day at a time. I think a lot of

00:06:00.080 --> 00:06:02.469
people start acting weird

00:06:02.469 --> 00:06:02.479
or

00:06:02.479 --> 00:06:05.670
flaky because

00:06:05.680 --> 00:06:08.950
they're impatient. It takes development.

00:06:08.960 --> 00:06:11.990
Back in the

00:06:11.990 --> 00:06:12.000
sixties

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:13.590
and

00:06:13.590 --> 00:06:13.600
seventies,

00:06:13.600 --> 00:06:16.710
mom used to tell

00:06:16.720 --> 00:06:18.309
me about it. You used to have the

00:06:18.319 --> 00:06:20.230
one-hour MotoPhoto. That was

00:06:20.240 --> 00:06:22.150
when we were kids. You could go

00:06:22.160 --> 00:06:24.309
and get your pictures done within an

00:06:24.319 --> 00:06:26.070
hour, and we were excited to get those in an

00:06:26.070 --> 00:06:26.080
hour.

00:06:26.080 --> 00:06:28.550
At first, it took about a week to

00:06:28.560 --> 00:06:31.110
go get your pictures done at

00:06:31.120 --> 00:06:34.390
Walmart or at the Kodak store.

00:06:34.400 --> 00:06:36.790
They had some kind of

00:06:36.800 --> 00:06:38.469
development center where you take

00:06:38.479 --> 00:06:40.950
your film. It took

00:06:40.960 --> 00:06:43.350
time, a process of developing those

00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:45.350
pictures. Then they came out with

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:48.390
Polaroids.

00:06:50.479 --> 00:06:52.230
You'd see things being developed

00:06:52.240 --> 00:06:53.670
really fast in front of your face. When

00:06:53.680 --> 00:06:55.029
I was a little boy, they got

00:06:55.039 --> 00:06:56.629
those Polaroid pictures and grandma would take

00:06:56.629 --> 00:06:56.639
them

00:06:56.639 --> 00:06:57.670
for our birthdays.

00:06:58.639 --> 00:07:00.629
She'd hand you those

00:07:00.639 --> 00:07:05.189
photos and we got so accustomed to

00:07:05.199 --> 00:07:07.430
wanting things so quickly. We want it

00:07:07.440 --> 00:07:09.909
right now. There's a process of

00:07:09.919 --> 00:07:12.629
development. Whenever you're taking

00:07:12.639 --> 00:07:15.029
a picture of your life and you look at

00:07:15.039 --> 00:07:17.110
yourself, you change.

00:07:17.120 --> 00:07:18.790
We go from glory to glory, but

00:07:18.800 --> 00:07:19.990
we have to be patient.

00:07:19.990 --> 00:07:20.000
There

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:21.270
are

00:07:21.280 --> 00:07:22.629
no shortcuts. Now we're used to

00:07:22.629 --> 00:07:22.639
the

00:07:22.639 --> 00:07:24.629
iPhone

00:07:24.639 --> 00:07:26.309
click and it's there. You can

00:07:26.319 --> 00:07:28.070
download it and send it to Australia in

00:07:28.080 --> 00:07:30.309
seconds.

00:07:30.319 --> 00:07:32.550
It doesn't take

00:07:32.560 --> 00:07:35.029
any time at all because

00:07:35.039 --> 00:07:37.110
we're so accustomed to having it right

00:07:37.120 --> 00:07:40.230
then. But there is a development in the

00:07:40.240 --> 00:07:42.629
spirit. There's a development in your

00:07:42.639 --> 00:07:45.830
walk with Jesus that takes time. It is

00:07:45.840 --> 00:07:47.430
not something that you're going to get

00:07:47.440 --> 00:07:51.029
overnight. It is a trial.

00:07:51.039 --> 00:07:53.350
There is

00:07:53.360 --> 00:07:55.110
a refiner's fire that

00:07:55.120 --> 00:07:56.950
comes with your development, walking with

00:07:56.960 --> 00:08:00.309
Jesus, hearing Him,

00:08:00.319 --> 00:08:03.029
knowing Him intimately, and following His

00:08:03.039 --> 00:08:05.270
voice. It's a development like the old

00:08:05.280 --> 00:08:06.469
way you did your film.

00:08:06.479 --> 00:08:08.790
And the Bible says if you seek, He'll

00:08:08.800 --> 00:08:11.510
knock, and Seek

00:08:11.510 --> 00:08:11.520
ye

00:08:11.520 --> 00:08:12.790
first the kingdom of God.

00:08:12.800 --> 00:08:14.150
Knock, and the door will be opened to him.

00:08:14.160 --> 00:08:16.869
Seek, and you shall find. I

00:08:16.879 --> 00:08:19.189
believe with all my heart that people are

00:08:19.199 --> 00:08:21.830
wanting that instantaneous drive-thru

00:08:21.840 --> 00:08:23.990
Christianity.

00:08:25.280 --> 00:08:26.710
They want to hit you in the head

00:08:26.720 --> 00:08:28.390
with a cheeseburger as you drive by

00:08:28.400 --> 00:08:29.350
because you don't even want to chew it

00:08:29.360 --> 00:08:32.230
up anymore.

00:08:32.240 --> 00:08:34.469
Open the window, the carhop goes at

00:08:34.479 --> 00:08:37.110
you and hits your head, and you keep driving

00:08:37.120 --> 00:08:38.870
because you don't even want to chew.

00:08:38.880 --> 00:08:41.350
We've got to slow down

00:08:41.360 --> 00:08:43.589
and realize that development with Jesus

00:08:43.599 --> 00:08:46.150
takes time. Just like

00:08:46.160 --> 00:08:48.150
anything worth doing is worth

00:08:48.160 --> 00:08:50.310
doing well and doing right.

00:08:50.320 --> 00:08:52.389
Following that

00:08:52.399 --> 00:08:55.430
still, small voice

00:08:55.430 --> 00:08:55.440
in

00:08:55.440 --> 00:08:58.389
your day-to-day life is key. If you

00:08:58.399 --> 00:09:01.990
have a check,

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:04.150
follow that

00:09:04.160 --> 00:09:06.389
peace that passes all understanding.

00:09:06.389 --> 00:09:06.399
If

00:09:06.399 --> 00:09:08.230
somebody comes up to you

00:09:08.240 --> 00:09:10.470
and says, "Listen, I've got this

00:09:10.480 --> 00:09:13.190
investment opportunity for you,"and you

00:09:13.200 --> 00:09:15.350
instantaneously have a

00:09:15.350 --> 00:09:15.360
feeling

00:09:15.360 --> 00:09:16.949
of

00:09:16.949 --> 00:09:16.959
irritation—it

00:09:16.959 --> 00:09:19.350
just

00:09:19.360 --> 00:09:21.269
weighs heavy and

00:09:21.269 --> 00:09:21.279
doesn't

00:09:21.279 --> 00:09:24.070
feel right—you know

00:09:24.080 --> 00:09:25.430
there's something not right about it.

00:09:25.440 --> 00:09:27.910
You could study it, but

00:09:27.920 --> 00:09:29.750
the Holy Spirit

00:09:29.760 --> 00:09:31.430
could be leading you to have peace

00:09:31.430 --> 00:09:31.440
while

00:09:31.440 --> 00:09:34.470
you reason in your mind.

00:09:34.480 --> 00:09:35.670
You feel a

00:09:35.680 --> 00:09:36.310
prompting

00:09:36.320 --> 00:09:38.710
in your spirit to do something, but you

00:09:38.720 --> 00:09:40.230
reason

00:09:40.240 --> 00:09:42.150
yourself out of the blessing because

00:09:42.160 --> 00:09:44.470
you try to add your intellect to the

00:09:44.480 --> 00:09:47.030
things of the Spirit. You can't do

00:09:47.040 --> 00:09:49.750
that because He sees more in the future

00:09:49.760 --> 00:09:52.070
than what you know of your past. He

00:09:52.080 --> 00:09:54.070
knows the

00:09:54.080 --> 00:09:56.630
great inventions and creative ideas to

00:09:56.640 --> 00:09:58.710
get wealth, but you will reason in your

00:09:58.720 --> 00:10:03.750
mind and cause a complete

00:10:03.760 --> 00:10:05.590
meltdown because you're trying to

00:10:05.600 --> 00:10:09.030
think, "Is this really God?"When you have

00:10:09.040 --> 00:10:10.550
that peace and that green

00:10:10.560 --> 00:10:11.910
light, but then you say, "I

00:10:11.920 --> 00:10:13.750
don't feel like I should do

00:10:13.760 --> 00:10:15.269
this,"you're

00:10:15.279 --> 00:10:17.670
using your intellect to try to navigate

00:10:17.680 --> 00:10:19.350
through the Spirit. You can't do

00:10:19.360 --> 00:10:21.829
that. You have to get in the Spirit when

00:10:21.839 --> 00:10:24.550
it comes to hearing Him and get out of

00:10:24.560 --> 00:10:27.110
your flesh.

00:10:27.120 --> 00:10:29.750
Say you're dating somebody and

00:10:29.760 --> 00:10:33.190
you feel this

00:10:33.190 --> 00:10:33.200
person

00:10:33.200 --> 00:10:36.150
is the cat's meow, the best

00:10:36.160 --> 00:10:38.069
thing ever, but then you feel a check

00:10:38.079 --> 00:10:39.350
about that person. The Lord is telling

00:10:39.360 --> 00:10:41.990
you not to marry them. You're like,

00:10:42.000 --> 00:10:44.230
"Well, they look so handsome

00:10:44.240 --> 00:10:47.670
or beautiful, and I really feel

00:10:47.680 --> 00:10:50.230
this is God."But you're looking at the

00:10:50.240 --> 00:10:52.550
outward appearance. They

00:10:52.560 --> 00:10:54.150
are just really nice-looking people,

00:10:54.150 --> 00:10:54.160
and

00:10:54.160 --> 00:10:55.590
you start

00:10:55.600 --> 00:10:57.269
questioning that inward check because the Holy

00:10:57.279 --> 00:10:58.470
Spirit said, "Don't marry

00:10:58.470 --> 00:10:58.480
them."You

00:10:58.480 --> 00:10:59.990
don't see the intent of their

00:11:00.000 --> 00:11:02.470
heart; this is going to wind up in a

00:11:02.480 --> 00:11:05.670
disaster. He's warning you: "Do not be

00:11:05.680 --> 00:11:08.230
unequally yoked with an unbeliever."You

00:11:08.230 --> 00:11:08.240
might think,

00:11:08.240 --> 00:11:10.790
"I can get them saved; we

00:11:10.800 --> 00:11:12.230
can date and I'll get them

00:11:12.230 --> 00:11:12.240
saved."You

00:11:12.240 --> 00:11:13.670
think

00:11:13.680 --> 00:11:15.829
after a

00:11:15.839 --> 00:11:17.350
couple of dates, if you lead them to

00:11:17.360 --> 00:11:19.350
Jesus, then they'll be a Christian and everything

00:11:19.350 --> 00:11:19.360
will

00:11:19.360 --> 00:11:21.750
be

00:11:21.750 --> 00:11:21.760
alright.

00:11:21.760 --> 00:11:24.310
But

00:11:24.320 --> 00:11:26.470
the Bible strictly says, "Do not be

00:11:26.480 --> 00:11:28.870
unequally yoked with an

00:11:28.870 --> 00:11:28.880
unbeliever."The

00:11:28.880 --> 00:11:30.870
Word is already guiding

00:11:30.880 --> 00:11:33.190
you.

00:11:33.200 --> 00:11:35.430
That's the ultimate voice—the Word of

00:11:35.440 --> 00:11:36.069
God.

00:11:36.640 --> 00:11:39.750
If the Word says it, that's all you

00:11:39.760 --> 00:11:40.949
need to know.

00:11:40.959 --> 00:11:43.509
Read the scriptures;

00:11:43.509 --> 00:11:43.519
look

00:11:43.519 --> 00:11:46.069
things up about

00:11:46.079 --> 00:11:48.790
marriage

00:11:48.790 --> 00:11:48.800
or

00:11:48.800 --> 00:11:50.870
finances. That is the

00:11:50.880 --> 00:11:52.150
ultimate authority,

00:11:52.160 --> 00:11:53.990
even beyond your peace.

00:11:54.000 --> 00:11:55.829
If the Bible says you can have it, you can.

00:11:57.360 --> 00:11:59.190
If it says don't do it, don't do it.

00:11:59.200 --> 00:12:00.470
It's that simple.

00:12:00.470 --> 00:12:00.480
Fornication

00:12:00.480 --> 00:12:03.110
and adultery

00:12:03.110 --> 00:12:03.120
are

00:12:03.120 --> 00:12:04.710
wrong;

00:12:04.720 --> 00:12:06.310
the Bible says don't do it.

00:12:06.320 --> 00:12:08.629
Staying pure sexually

00:12:08.629 --> 00:12:08.639
is

00:12:08.639 --> 00:12:10.710
all there.

00:12:10.720 --> 00:12:12.310
Following the voice of the Lord for your

00:12:12.310 --> 00:12:12.320
life—that

00:12:12.320 --> 00:12:14.550
is the manual we go by. When

00:12:14.550 --> 00:12:14.560
you have

00:12:14.560 --> 00:12:17.350
the Word

00:12:17.350 --> 00:12:17.360
and

00:12:17.360 --> 00:12:19.910
peace combined, it's

00:12:19.920 --> 00:12:21.590
unfailing;

00:12:21.600 --> 00:12:24.150
it is the perfect

00:12:24.160 --> 00:12:26.470
path for your life. Whenever it

00:12:26.480 --> 00:12:29.670
says, "Do not be unequally

00:12:29.670 --> 00:12:29.680
yoked

00:12:29.680 --> 00:12:32.230
with

00:12:32.240 --> 00:12:33.110
unbelievers,"it's

00:12:33.120 --> 00:12:35.030
just God trying to protect you.

00:12:35.030 --> 00:12:35.040
It

00:12:35.040 --> 00:12:36.389
doesn't

00:12:36.399 --> 00:12:38.550
matter about the beauty;

00:12:38.560 --> 00:12:41.990
find a woman or a man who loves

00:12:42.000 --> 00:12:44.069
the Lord their God with all their heart,

00:12:44.079 --> 00:12:45.829
mind, soul, and

00:12:45.839 --> 00:12:49.350
strength.

00:12:49.360 --> 00:12:51.269
Your road is going to be a lot

00:12:51.279 --> 00:12:51.990
easier.

00:12:52.000 --> 00:12:54.230
It's crucial in

00:12:54.240 --> 00:12:55.829
these last days.

00:12:56.310 --> 00:12:56.320
If

00:12:57.120 --> 00:12:58.470
you say,

00:12:58.480 --> 00:13:00.150
"I don't have anybody like that around

00:13:01.750 --> 00:13:01.760
me,"make

00:13:05.120 --> 00:13:07.990
your petition unto God. Write down

00:13:08.000 --> 00:13:09.190
what you're believing for:

00:13:09.680 --> 00:13:11.269
a godly

00:13:11.279 --> 00:13:13.509
spouse, a

00:13:13.519 --> 00:13:15.430
house, or whatever.

00:13:15.440 --> 00:13:17.590
Write those things down and make it

00:13:17.600 --> 00:13:18.629
plain.

00:13:19.120 --> 00:13:20.710
Put it on your refrigerator,

00:13:22.000 --> 00:13:23.829
your bathroom mirror,

00:13:23.829 --> 00:13:23.839
or

00:13:23.839 --> 00:13:26.870
your car visor—someplace where you

00:13:26.880 --> 00:13:30.470
can see it all the time.

00:13:30.480 --> 00:13:32.629
Let that

00:13:32.639 --> 00:13:35.030
be a reminder. Then pray over it,

00:13:35.040 --> 00:13:36.550
put your hand on it, and say, "I believe, I

00:13:36.560 --> 00:13:37.590
receive."Faith

00:13:37.600 --> 00:13:39.269
calls those things that be not as

00:13:39.279 --> 00:13:40.470
though they were.

00:13:40.480 --> 00:13:42.389
I believe with all my heart, Father,

00:13:42.389 --> 00:13:42.399
that

00:13:42.399 --> 00:13:44.150
You said You supply all my needs

00:13:44.160 --> 00:13:45.590
according to Your riches in glory by

00:13:45.600 --> 00:13:48.069
Christ Jesus. Every need is not just

00:13:48.079 --> 00:13:49.509
financial;

00:13:49.519 --> 00:13:51.430
it's physical, spiritual,

00:13:51.430 --> 00:13:51.440
mental, and emotional.

00:13:51.440 --> 00:13:54.069
It's whatever you need

00:13:54.079 --> 00:13:56.230
to operate in abundance

00:13:56.230 --> 00:13:56.240
until

00:13:56.240 --> 00:13:58.310
it overflows. Growing

00:13:58.310 --> 00:13:58.320
up, my

00:13:58.320 --> 00:14:00.550
mom and

00:14:00.550 --> 00:14:00.560
dad and

00:14:00.560 --> 00:14:03.750
I would

00:14:03.750 --> 00:14:03.760
find

00:14:03.760 --> 00:14:05.509
a house we

00:14:05.519 --> 00:14:07.990
knew we could afford, go to

00:14:07.990 --> 00:14:08.000
the property,

00:14:08.000 --> 00:14:09.509
and lay hands

00:14:09.509 --> 00:14:09.519
on it.

00:14:09.519 --> 00:14:11.430
We would

00:14:15.519 --> 00:14:16.550
say,

00:14:16.560 --> 00:14:19.829
"Father, I thank You that we have favor

00:14:19.839 --> 00:14:21.829
to find a house like this."I'm not

00:14:21.839 --> 00:14:23.350
saying go around coveting

00:14:23.350 --> 00:14:23.360
everyone's

00:14:23.360 --> 00:14:24.790
houses. If it's not for sale, don't

00:14:24.800 --> 00:14:25.990
do

00:14:26.000 --> 00:14:27.750
weird stuff.

00:14:27.750 --> 00:14:27.760
But

00:14:27.760 --> 00:14:29.430
if the house is for

00:14:29.440 --> 00:14:31.430
sale, say, "Father, I

00:14:31.440 --> 00:14:33.750
thank You for open doors of opportunity

00:14:33.760 --> 00:14:36.310
to purchase this home.

00:14:38.720 --> 00:14:40.949
You said You'd give me the desires of my

00:14:40.959 --> 00:14:43.430
heart, and I thank You that You

00:14:43.440 --> 00:14:46.470
are the God of more than

00:14:46.470 --> 00:14:46.480
enough."Lay

00:14:46.480 --> 00:14:48.389
hands on that piece of land and

00:14:48.399 --> 00:14:50.230
believe you receive it in the name of

00:14:50.240 --> 00:14:52.310
Jesus. Believe by faith.

00:14:55.360 --> 00:14:56.870
If

00:14:56.880 --> 00:14:58.790
you feel a leading and the Lord tells you

00:14:58.800 --> 00:15:00.310
this is your piece of property,

00:15:03.440 --> 00:15:05.350
stand on the Word.

00:15:05.360 --> 00:15:07.590
Find scriptures that pertain to what

00:15:07.600 --> 00:15:10.389
you're believing for and use that as

00:15:10.399 --> 00:15:13.189
your foundation. Then

00:15:13.199 --> 00:15:14.629
find that peace. If you don't have

00:15:14.629 --> 00:15:14.639
peace

00:15:14.639 --> 00:15:16.550
about it, don't go with it.

00:15:16.560 --> 00:15:19.269
But if you have peace, follow it.

00:15:19.279 --> 00:15:20.710
We do

00:15:20.720 --> 00:15:22.230
it all the time. "Father, I thank

00:15:22.240 --> 00:15:24.550
You that You said You provide for us. I

00:15:24.560 --> 00:15:25.750
thank You, God, that You're going to

00:15:25.760 --> 00:15:27.509
take care of us and

00:15:27.519 --> 00:15:29.430
do the things You

00:15:29.440 --> 00:15:31.990
said in Your

00:15:31.990 --> 00:15:32.000
Word."That's

00:15:32.000 --> 00:15:34.069
where we stand. There

00:15:34.069 --> 00:15:34.079
were many

00:15:34.079 --> 00:15:36.629
times

00:15:40.399 --> 00:15:43.750
in the

00:15:43.760 --> 00:15:45.829
past when I followed a spirit of

00:15:45.839 --> 00:15:48.470
heaviness. I would

00:15:48.470 --> 00:15:48.480
be

00:15:48.480 --> 00:15:50.069
walking around and feel

00:15:50.069 --> 00:15:50.079
an

00:15:50.079 --> 00:15:53.030
urge to

00:15:53.040 --> 00:15:53.749
pray, thinking

00:15:53.749 --> 00:15:53.759
I had

00:15:53.759 --> 00:15:55.590
to pray all the time.

00:15:55.600 --> 00:15:56.629
Yeah.

00:15:56.639 --> 00:15:58.629
Because don't you just feel that? I used

00:15:58.639 --> 00:15:59.030
to.

00:15:59.040 --> 00:16:00.629
I felt like impending doom

00:16:00.639 --> 00:16:02.790
all the time. Well, I

00:16:02.800 --> 00:16:04.629
feel there's a terrorist attack coming.

00:16:04.639 --> 00:16:06.949
I feel this coming and everything.

00:16:06.959 --> 00:16:08.710
Well, you know, I've got to pray over

00:16:08.720 --> 00:16:10.870
this. I feel that

00:16:10.880 --> 00:16:12.870
there's going to be some kind of major

00:16:12.880 --> 00:16:14.870
weather event or an earthquake. And you

00:16:14.880 --> 00:16:19.269
walk around in this fear bubble because

00:16:19.279 --> 00:16:20.949
I'm an intercessor. That's

00:16:20.959 --> 00:16:22.230
supposed to happen; I'm supposed to be

00:16:22.240 --> 00:16:24.470
praying. And the Lord addressed it one

00:16:24.480 --> 00:16:26.790
day and he told me, 'Brandon,

00:16:26.800 --> 00:16:29.189
what are you doing?'And I said,

00:16:29.199 --> 00:16:31.590
'Well, I'm interceding, Lord. I

00:16:31.600 --> 00:16:32.949
said there's a heaviness. You're

00:16:32.959 --> 00:16:35.030
calling me to pray.'He said, 'No, that

00:16:35.040 --> 00:16:37.749
is a spirit of

00:16:37.749 --> 00:16:37.759
forebodings

00:16:37.759 --> 00:16:40.790
that is tormenting you, Brandon. I want

00:16:40.800 --> 00:16:42.550
you to live life in abundance to the full

00:16:42.550 --> 00:16:42.560
until

00:16:42.560 --> 00:16:44.629
it overflows. And you are not

00:16:44.639 --> 00:16:47.269
doing that. You are living underneath a

00:16:47.279 --> 00:16:50.069
dark shadow. My yoke is easy and my

00:16:50.079 --> 00:16:52.629
burden is light.'And that's where he

00:16:52.639 --> 00:16:55.430
was saying to me, 'You're

00:16:55.440 --> 00:16:57.670
living underneath a

00:16:57.670 --> 00:16:57.680
burden.'And

00:16:57.680 --> 00:16:59.990
my wife can testify to it; I

00:16:59.990 --> 00:17:00.000
lived

00:17:00.000 --> 00:17:01.590
that way. I felt like I was in

00:17:01.600 --> 00:17:03.030
tears all the time walking. I'm

00:17:03.040 --> 00:17:04.470
interceding for somebody, I don't know

00:17:04.480 --> 00:17:05.669
who it is.

00:17:05.679 --> 00:17:07.510
And I would walk around acting so

00:17:07.520 --> 00:17:09.590
spiritual, like I was praying all the

00:17:09.600 --> 00:17:11.510
time at work, at church, or wherever.

00:17:11.520 --> 00:17:13.189
And people would ask, 'Are you okay today,

00:17:13.199 --> 00:17:15.110
Brother Brandon?''Oh, no, man. I've got

00:17:15.120 --> 00:17:17.270
the burden to pray. I've got a burden to

00:17:17.270 --> 00:17:17.280
pray.'And

00:17:17.280 --> 00:17:18.710
it

00:17:18.710 --> 00:17:18.720
sounded

00:17:18.720 --> 00:17:20.069
like you were doing something so

00:17:20.079 --> 00:17:22.549
spiritual and it was the

00:17:22.559 --> 00:17:23.909
flesh. It was a demonic spirit

00:17:23.919 --> 00:17:26.870
tormenting you because fear has torment. But

00:17:26.880 --> 00:17:29.270
perfect love casteth out all fear. And

00:17:29.280 --> 00:17:30.630
I'm telling you, a spirit of

00:17:30.630 --> 00:17:30.640
forebodings

00:17:30.640 --> 00:17:32.950
to get on you as a believer

00:17:32.960 --> 00:17:34.870
because you think you're doing good by

00:17:34.880 --> 00:17:37.110
thinking you're praying. But

00:17:37.120 --> 00:17:39.110
the Lord wants you to have joy, ladies

00:17:39.120 --> 00:17:41.190
and gentlemen. The Bible said he

00:17:41.200 --> 00:17:43.830
wants you to have exceedingly abundantly

00:17:43.840 --> 00:17:45.669
above all that you ask or think, but in

00:17:45.679 --> 00:17:49.270
joy unspeakable and full of glory. The

00:17:49.280 --> 00:17:51.270
joy of the Lord is our strength. There's

00:17:51.280 --> 00:17:53.590
so many things about joy and walking in

00:17:53.600 --> 00:17:55.430
peace that passes all understanding. So,

00:17:55.440 --> 00:17:57.510
I just felt in my spirit,

00:17:57.520 --> 00:17:59.590
because I know a lot of intercessory

00:17:59.600 --> 00:18:02.549
prayer people follow my channel, that if

00:18:02.559 --> 00:18:04.710
you walk around with heaviness all the

00:18:04.720 --> 00:18:08.310
time, check it. And this is what I do:

00:18:08.320 --> 00:18:09.990
'Father,

00:18:10.000 --> 00:18:12.710
if this is you praying,'and I question

00:18:12.710 --> 00:18:12.720
it—I'm

00:18:12.720 --> 00:18:14.230
just trying to teach you how to

00:18:14.240 --> 00:18:16.630
do it—'Father, if this is you telling me

00:18:16.640 --> 00:18:19.510
to intercede for something, then speak

00:18:19.520 --> 00:18:21.830
on. But if this is a spirit of

00:18:21.830 --> 00:18:21.840
forebodings,

00:18:21.840 --> 00:18:25.029
a tormenting spirit of fear,

00:18:25.039 --> 00:18:27.270
I bind it right now in the name of

00:18:27.280 --> 00:18:29.190
Jesus and I cast you out. You get out

00:18:29.200 --> 00:18:32.310
of here and you leave me alone. I will

00:18:32.320 --> 00:18:34.549
not walk in a spirit of torment and

00:18:34.559 --> 00:18:38.390
fear, but 2 Timothy

00:18:38.400 --> 00:18:39.430
1:7

00:18:39.440 --> 00:18:41.350
says that God has not given me a spirit

00:18:41.360 --> 00:18:44.390
of fear, but of power and of love and of

00:18:44.400 --> 00:18:47.669
a well-balanced mind, and I will walk

00:18:47.679 --> 00:18:50.549
in a balanced mind in no

00:18:50.549 --> 00:18:50.559
fear.'So,

00:18:50.559 --> 00:18:52.310
Father, if this is you and you're

00:18:52.320 --> 00:18:54.310
warning me to pray about something, then

00:18:54.320 --> 00:18:57.430
speak on. But if it is not, I command

00:18:57.440 --> 00:19:00.789
this spirit to get out of here now and

00:19:00.789 --> 00:19:00.799
address

00:19:00.799 --> 00:19:02.870
it just like that. And the moment

00:19:02.880 --> 00:19:05.350
you start doing that,

00:19:05.360 --> 00:19:07.510
you'll feel even more of a tug

00:19:07.520 --> 00:19:09.110
because the Holy Spirit is the one

00:19:09.120 --> 00:19:10.789
leading you and guiding you into all

00:19:10.799 --> 00:19:12.950
things. He's trying to protect you.

00:19:12.960 --> 00:19:14.950
He wants you to live that life in

00:19:14.960 --> 00:19:16.870
abundance. So he's going to tell you,

00:19:16.880 --> 00:19:19.029
'That's me. That's me. You better pray

00:19:19.039 --> 00:19:20.470
now. Come on, let's jump in the river

00:19:20.470 --> 00:19:20.480
together,'and

00:19:20.480 --> 00:19:22.470
you just go in

00:19:22.480 --> 00:19:24.549
that because then you'll know this is

00:19:24.559 --> 00:19:26.470
the Holy Spirit really trying to lead me

00:19:26.480 --> 00:19:28.549
and he's trying to help me because he

00:19:28.559 --> 00:19:30.549
wants you to follow that peace.

00:19:30.559 --> 00:19:32.630
And so I hope that helped with that. I

00:19:32.640 --> 00:19:34.150
really feel like it's important. I feel

00:19:34.160 --> 00:19:35.909
like I'm talking to somebody about this

00:19:35.919 --> 00:19:37.510
because the Lord put that on my heart

00:19:37.520 --> 00:19:40.310
right then to tell you: do not let a

00:19:40.320 --> 00:19:43.830
spirit of torment push you around.

00:19:43.840 --> 00:19:46.070
You have authority over the devil

00:19:46.080 --> 00:19:48.390
and you don't have to walk in fear in

00:19:48.400 --> 00:19:50.870
any area of your life about any

00:19:50.880 --> 00:19:52.390
calamity.

00:19:52.400 --> 00:19:54.390
We are the victors,

00:19:54.400 --> 00:19:56.950
not the victims. So I want my wife to

00:19:56.960 --> 00:19:59.350
read this to you. This is an amazing

00:19:59.360 --> 00:20:01.830
book. You know, we were at prayer on

00:20:01.840 --> 00:20:05.190
Sunday at church, which

00:20:05.200 --> 00:20:07.909
was amazing. Every single time we go, we

00:20:07.919 --> 00:20:10.390
get refilled. We go and

00:20:10.400 --> 00:20:12.470
participate at the Glorious Church

00:20:12.480 --> 00:20:16.950
Fellowship prayer a lot.

00:20:16.960 --> 00:20:19.350
If you're looking for

00:20:19.360 --> 00:20:21.270
people that want to jump in

00:20:21.280 --> 00:20:23.110
the river, we look for it all

00:20:23.120 --> 00:20:25.750
the time, listening to Lynne Hammond

00:20:25.760 --> 00:20:29.110
online at Living Word

00:20:29.110 --> 00:20:29.120
in

00:20:29.120 --> 00:20:31.830
Minneapolis, Minnesota, and the prayer

00:20:31.840 --> 00:20:35.430
conference,

00:20:35.440 --> 00:20:37.590
wanting to grow ourselves spiritually in

00:20:37.600 --> 00:20:40.950
prayer. Pastor

00:20:40.960 --> 00:20:43.190
Candace leads that prayer group at

00:20:43.190 --> 00:20:43.200
The

00:20:43.200 --> 00:20:46.310
Glory's Church, and they're anointed.

00:20:46.320 --> 00:20:48.630
We used to listen to a lot

00:20:48.640 --> 00:20:50.710
of other prayer groups and we still do.

00:20:50.720 --> 00:20:52.870
But I would encourage everybody, if

00:20:52.880 --> 00:20:54.230
you want to grow spiritually, you've got

00:20:54.240 --> 00:20:56.789
to listen to prayer people. You've got

00:20:56.799 --> 00:20:59.430
to feed your spirit

00:20:59.440 --> 00:21:01.029
just like faith cometh by hearing and

00:21:01.039 --> 00:21:02.870
hearing by the word of God. You've got

00:21:02.880 --> 00:21:06.630
to feed your spirit so you'll grow

00:21:06.640 --> 00:21:07.350
in that area

00:21:07.360 --> 00:21:08.710
and in prayer.

00:21:08.720 --> 00:21:11.270
It's like wanting to learn math and

00:21:11.280 --> 00:21:12.710
be really good at it, but you

00:21:12.720 --> 00:21:14.070
never go to math classes.

00:21:14.080 --> 00:21:17.029
Yeah, that's exactly right, babe.

00:21:17.039 --> 00:21:18.710
And then you're taking a

00:21:18.720 --> 00:21:21.110
spelling class trying to learn math

00:21:21.120 --> 00:21:23.029
and you're hoping you'll just catch math

00:21:23.039 --> 00:21:24.230
along the way. No,

00:21:24.240 --> 00:21:25.669
but you never go to math class.

00:21:25.679 --> 00:21:27.510
So, this is where I'm saying we

00:21:27.520 --> 00:21:29.510
find books.

00:21:29.520 --> 00:21:31.110
When I went to prayer on

00:21:31.120 --> 00:21:33.029
Sunday, the Lord downloaded so much

00:21:33.039 --> 00:21:35.270
stuff to me and I walked away. I said,

00:21:35.280 --> 00:21:36.710
'Hey, babe. This is what the

00:21:36.720 --> 00:21:38.390
Lord said tonight in

00:21:38.400 --> 00:21:40.310
prayer.'And

00:21:40.320 --> 00:21:41.830
she said, 'That's

00:21:41.840 --> 00:21:44.070
exactly what he said to

00:21:44.070 --> 00:21:44.080
me.'And

00:21:44.080 --> 00:21:46.549
it was to help

00:21:46.559 --> 00:21:48.630
me out with helping this

00:21:48.640 --> 00:21:49.990
channel and things. And the Lord gave

00:21:50.000 --> 00:21:51.909
her... because I said, 'Lord,

00:21:51.919 --> 00:21:52.950
you're going to have to talk to Diana

00:21:52.960 --> 00:21:54.710
about this. I need your help with

00:21:54.710 --> 00:21:54.720
that.'We

00:21:54.720 --> 00:21:57.510
flow together on this

00:21:57.520 --> 00:21:59.190
because I wanted this to flow

00:21:59.190 --> 00:21:59.200
perfectly.

00:21:59.200 --> 00:22:00.789
And she said, 'He's already told me,

00:22:00.789 --> 00:22:00.799
hun.'She

00:22:00.799 --> 00:22:04.149
said,

00:22:04.159 --> 00:22:07.029
'I heard him to get

00:22:07.039 --> 00:22:10.549
this book right here.'And so

00:22:10.559 --> 00:22:13.990
this is a

00:22:14.000 --> 00:22:16.390
book by Brother Hagin, but she was

00:22:16.400 --> 00:22:18.549
reading these chapters to me, and I want

00:22:18.559 --> 00:22:23.909
her to read this part right here.

00:22:23.919 --> 00:22:26.230
This is really important and

00:22:26.240 --> 00:22:28.070
let it minister to y'all because it goes

00:22:28.080 --> 00:22:29.350
along with what we're trying to teach

00:22:29.360 --> 00:22:31.750
you all, that Brother Hagin walked this

00:22:31.760 --> 00:22:35.110
out as a young believer and how

00:22:35.120 --> 00:22:37.270
he became a spiritual giant in

00:22:37.280 --> 00:22:39.430
my eyes. I mean, I don't see anybody in

00:22:39.440 --> 00:22:41.990
the natural that heard the Lord

00:22:41.990 --> 00:22:42.000
as

00:22:42.000 --> 00:22:43.909
clear in this generation.

00:22:45.360 --> 00:22:48.950
Yeah. So he had an open-eyed vision

00:22:48.950 --> 00:22:48.960
and

00:22:48.960 --> 00:22:52.310
he saw Jesus come and

00:22:52.320 --> 00:22:54.070
sit by his bed and he talked to him for

00:22:54.080 --> 00:22:56.870
an hour and a half. And this says

00:22:56.880 --> 00:22:59.510
Jesus said to me: 'The prophet of the

00:22:59.520 --> 00:23:02.230
New Testament is very similar to the

00:23:02.240 --> 00:23:04.470
prophet of the Old Testament in that the

00:23:04.480 --> 00:23:06.710
prophet of the Old Testament was called

00:23:06.720 --> 00:23:09.909
a seer because he saw and knew

00:23:09.919 --> 00:23:11.830
things supernaturally.

00:23:11.840 --> 00:23:14.470
The prophet of the New Testament also

00:23:14.480 --> 00:23:17.029
sees and knows things supernaturally.

00:23:17.039 --> 00:23:19.110
But the prophet of the New Testament

00:23:19.120 --> 00:23:21.510
does not have the same status as the

00:23:21.520 --> 00:23:24.310
prophet of the Old Testament in that I

00:23:24.320 --> 00:23:26.950
did not set prophets in the church to

00:23:26.960 --> 00:23:28.230
guide the church.

00:23:28.640 --> 00:23:31.350
A Christian under the New Testament need

00:23:31.360 --> 00:23:33.750
not seek guidance through prophets.

00:23:34.320 --> 00:23:35.990
He might receive guidance through

00:23:36.000 --> 00:23:38.310
prophets, but he should not seek it. It

00:23:38.320 --> 00:23:40.630
is unscriptural to do so.

00:23:40.640 --> 00:23:42.789
The ministry of the New Testament

00:23:42.799 --> 00:23:45.590
prophet in this area is only to confirm

00:23:45.600 --> 00:23:47.909
what people already have in their own

00:23:47.919 --> 00:23:49.430
spirits.

00:23:49.440 --> 00:23:51.990
Under the Old Covenant, only the priest,

00:23:52.000 --> 00:23:54.070
the prophet, and the king were anointed

00:23:54.080 --> 00:23:56.149
by the Holy Spirit to stand in those

00:23:56.159 --> 00:23:59.350
offices. What you would call the

00:23:59.350 --> 00:23:59.360
laity

00:23:59.360 --> 00:24:01.669
did not have the spirit of God upon them

00:24:01.679 --> 00:24:04.230
or in them. Therefore, under the Old

00:24:04.240 --> 00:24:06.230
Covenant, people would seek guidance

00:24:06.240 --> 00:24:08.310
through the prophet because he had the

00:24:08.320 --> 00:24:11.110
spirit of God.'Under the New Testament,

00:24:11.120 --> 00:24:13.510
thanks be to God, we not only have the

00:24:13.520 --> 00:24:15.669
Spirit of God upon us, we have Him in

00:24:15.679 --> 00:24:19.110
us. Jesus also said to me, 'Under the New

00:24:19.120 --> 00:24:21.350
Covenant, it does not say, "As many as

00:24:21.360 --> 00:24:23.350
are led by prophets, they are the sons

00:24:23.360 --> 00:24:27.510
of God."The New Testament says, "For as

00:24:27.520 --> 00:24:30.549
many as are led by the Spirit of God,

00:24:30.559 --> 00:24:33.430
they are the sons of

00:24:33.430 --> 00:24:33.440
God."'See

00:24:33.440 --> 00:24:34.630
Romans.

00:24:34.640 --> 00:24:36.630
Get that scripture down inside of you.

00:24:36.640 --> 00:24:36.950
You

00:24:36.960 --> 00:24:38.390
read that again, baby. I love that

00:24:38.400 --> 00:24:39.029
scripture:

00:24:39.039 --> 00:24:41.510
'For as many as are led by the Spirit of

00:24:41.520 --> 00:24:43.590
God, they are the sons of

00:24:45.600 --> 00:24:47.269
God.'Romans.

00:24:48.640 --> 00:24:50.230
So, you're going to be led by the Spirit

00:24:50.240 --> 00:24:51.750
of God,

00:24:51.760 --> 00:24:53.350
and that shows you're a son of

00:24:53.350 --> 00:24:53.360
God—not

00:24:53.360 --> 00:24:55.430
led by a

00:24:55.440 --> 00:24:55.909
prophet,

00:24:56.480 --> 00:24:59.029
not led by your pastor,

00:24:59.029 --> 00:24:59.039
but

00:24:59.039 --> 00:25:01.830
by the Spirit of God. Now, He may use

00:25:01.840 --> 00:25:04.630
your pastor or use a prophetic voice to

00:25:04.640 --> 00:25:07.190
help you along the way, but it's to

00:25:07.200 --> 00:25:09.750
confirm some things; ultimately, it's

00:25:09.760 --> 00:25:12.630
on you

00:25:12.640 --> 00:25:14.789
by the Spirit of God in you. Does that

00:25:14.799 --> 00:25:15.510
make sense?

00:25:15.520 --> 00:25:16.870
Because that's biblical right

00:25:16.880 --> 00:25:17.190
there.

00:25:17.600 --> 00:25:20.470
Romans.

00:25:20.480 --> 00:25:23.669
Then He said, 'The number one way,

00:25:23.679 --> 00:25:26.710
the primary way that I lead all of my

00:25:26.720 --> 00:25:28.950
children, is by the inward

00:25:28.950 --> 00:25:28.960
witness.'I

00:25:28.960 --> 00:25:31.510
am going to show you how that

00:25:31.520 --> 00:25:33.350
works so you won't make the mistakes you

00:25:33.360 --> 00:25:36.310
have made in the past. Then He called my

00:25:36.320 --> 00:25:37.750
attention to something that had been

00:25:37.760 --> 00:25:40.070
happening to me for the previous three

00:25:40.080 --> 00:25:42.310
days. For the past three days, I had sat

00:25:42.320 --> 00:25:44.070
down to write a letter to a pastor

00:25:44.080 --> 00:25:45.990
confirming a date to hold a meeting for

00:25:46.000 --> 00:25:48.789
him. Somehow, the first day I got about

00:25:48.799 --> 00:25:50.630
half of a page, and then I tore it up

00:25:50.640 --> 00:25:52.230
and threw it in the wastebasket. The

00:25:52.240 --> 00:25:54.950
next day I did the same thing. The third

00:25:54.960 --> 00:25:57.110
day I did the same thing. Then it was

00:25:57.120 --> 00:25:58.710
the day that the Lord was here in the

00:25:58.720 --> 00:26:01.669
room talking to me. Jesus said, 'You see

00:26:01.679 --> 00:26:04.149
me sitting here talking to you. This is

00:26:04.159 --> 00:26:06.230
a manifestation of the Spirit called

00:26:06.240 --> 00:26:08.470
discerning of spirits.'Discerning of

00:26:08.480 --> 00:26:10.630
spirits is seeing into the spirit realm.

00:26:10.640 --> 00:26:12.310
This is the prophet's ministry

00:26:12.310 --> 00:26:12.320
in

00:26:12.320 --> 00:26:14.710
operation. You are seeing into the realm

00:26:14.720 --> 00:26:16.710
of the spirit. 'You see me, you hear me

00:26:16.720 --> 00:26:18.870
talking. I am bringing you through the

00:26:18.880 --> 00:26:20.789
vision a word of knowledge and also a

00:26:20.799 --> 00:26:23.190
word of wisdom. I am telling you not to

00:26:23.200 --> 00:26:25.590
go to that church. The pastor would not

00:26:25.600 --> 00:26:27.029
accept the way that you would

00:26:27.039 --> 00:26:29.190
minister when you got there. But I am

00:26:29.200 --> 00:26:31.350
never going to lead you this way

00:26:31.350 --> 00:26:31.360
again.'And

00:26:31.360 --> 00:26:32.950
He never has, and that was many

00:26:32.960 --> 00:26:35.269
years ago. 'From now on, I'm going to

00:26:35.279 --> 00:26:38.070
lead you by the inward witness.'You had

00:26:38.080 --> 00:26:40.630
the inward witness all the time. You had

00:26:40.640 --> 00:26:42.789
a check in your spirit. That's the

00:26:42.799 --> 00:26:44.390
reason you tore up the letter three

00:26:44.400 --> 00:26:47.110
times. You had something on the

00:26:47.110 --> 00:26:47.120
inside—a

00:26:47.120 --> 00:26:50.230
check, a red light, a stop signal. It

00:26:50.240 --> 00:26:51.830
wasn't even a voice that said, 'Don't

00:26:51.830 --> 00:26:51.840
go.'It

00:26:51.840 --> 00:26:54.789
was just an inward intuition.

00:26:54.799 --> 00:26:56.549
Then Jesus reminded me of another

00:26:56.559 --> 00:26:58.390
invitation. I had preached at a

00:26:58.400 --> 00:26:59.830
convention for one of the Full Gospel

00:26:59.840 --> 00:27:02.470
denominations the previous year. Nearly

00:27:02.480 --> 00:27:03.990
every pastor there asked me if I could

00:27:04.000 --> 00:27:06.070
come hold a meeting. I had hundreds of

00:27:06.080 --> 00:27:07.909
calls. One fellow came up to

00:27:07.919 --> 00:27:09.990
me and said, 'Brother Hagin, do you ever

00:27:10.000 --> 00:27:11.909
go to small churches?'I said, 'I go

00:27:11.919 --> 00:27:14.630
anywhere the Lord says to go.''Well, we

00:27:14.640 --> 00:27:16.950
only run about 70 to 90 in Sunday

00:27:16.960 --> 00:27:18.470
school, but if God ever speaks to you,

00:27:18.480 --> 00:27:20.630
we want you to come.'I dismissed that

00:27:20.640 --> 00:27:22.549
conversation along with many others.

00:27:22.559 --> 00:27:24.310
Several months later, however, while

00:27:24.320 --> 00:27:26.149
praying in the church one day about my

00:27:26.159 --> 00:27:28.470
services that night, that conversation

00:27:28.480 --> 00:27:30.789
came back to me. Then every day it

00:27:30.799 --> 00:27:33.110
continued to come back to me. Finally,

00:27:33.120 --> 00:27:35.110
after about 30 or 40 days, I said,

00:27:35.120 --> 00:27:36.950
'Lord, do you want me to go to that

00:27:36.960 --> 00:27:39.510
little church for a meeting?'The more I

00:27:39.520 --> 00:27:41.430
would pray about it, the more I would

00:27:41.440 --> 00:27:43.830
think about it, as we say, the better I

00:27:43.840 --> 00:27:46.310
would feel about it on the inside of me.

00:27:46.320 --> 00:27:48.470
It wasn't a physical feeling, but it was

00:27:48.480 --> 00:27:50.070
a feeling in my spirit—peace.

00:27:50.070 --> 00:27:50.080
Jesus,

00:27:50.080 --> 00:27:52.710
sitting by my bedside,

00:27:52.720 --> 00:27:55.350
referred to this: 'The more you thought

00:27:55.360 --> 00:27:58.310
about it, the better you felt about it.

00:27:58.320 --> 00:28:01.190
You had a velvety-like feeling in your

00:28:01.200 --> 00:28:02.149
spirit.

00:28:02.159 --> 00:28:04.389
That's the green light. That's the

00:28:04.399 --> 00:28:07.029
go-ahead signal. That's the witness of

00:28:07.039 --> 00:28:10.070
the Spirit to go. Now you see me sitting

00:28:10.080 --> 00:28:12.230
here, you hear me talking to you, and I'm

00:28:12.240 --> 00:28:14.630
telling you to go to that church. But I

00:28:14.640 --> 00:28:16.230
am never going to lead you to go

00:28:16.240 --> 00:28:18.950
anywhere like this again.'He never has.

00:28:18.960 --> 00:28:21.909
'From now on, I'm going to lead you just

00:28:21.919 --> 00:28:24.230
like I do every other Christian: by the

00:28:24.240 --> 00:28:25.590
inward

00:28:25.600 --> 00:28:27.830
witness.'Then

00:28:27.840 --> 00:28:30.070
the Lord said this to me, which is

00:28:30.080 --> 00:28:31.990
not just for my benefit, but also for

00:28:32.000 --> 00:28:35.110
yours: 'If you will learn to follow that

00:28:35.120 --> 00:28:38.389
inward witness, I will make you rich. I

00:28:38.399 --> 00:28:40.389
will guide you in all the affairs of

00:28:40.399 --> 00:28:43.190
life, financial as well as

00:28:43.190 --> 00:28:43.200
spiritual.'Some

00:28:43.200 --> 00:28:45.029
think God is only interested in

00:28:45.039 --> 00:28:46.789
their spiritual well-being and nothing

00:28:46.799 --> 00:28:49.110
else, but He is interested in everything

00:28:49.120 --> 00:28:51.830
we are interested in. 'I am not opposed

00:28:51.840 --> 00:28:54.230
to my children being rich; I'm opposed

00:28:54.240 --> 00:28:56.549
to their being

00:28:56.549 --> 00:28:56.559
covetous.'I

00:28:56.559 --> 00:28:58.630
have followed that inward witness, and

00:28:58.640 --> 00:29:00.070
He has done just what He said He would

00:29:00.080 --> 00:29:02.389
do. He has made me rich. Someone said,

00:29:02.399 --> 00:29:04.310
'Are you a millionaire?'I didn't say

00:29:04.320 --> 00:29:06.149
that. Some people fail to realize

00:29:06.159 --> 00:29:08.389
what the word rich means.

00:29:08.399 --> 00:29:11.510
It means a full supply. It means

00:29:11.520 --> 00:29:13.990
abundant provision. I have more than a

00:29:14.000 --> 00:29:15.830
full supply. I have more than abundant

00:29:15.840 --> 00:29:18.230
provision. It is because I learned to

00:29:18.240 --> 00:29:20.310
follow the leading of the Spirit by the

00:29:20.320 --> 00:29:23.350
inward witness. What He did for me, He

00:29:23.360 --> 00:29:25.510
will do for you. It won't come overnight

00:29:25.520 --> 00:29:27.590
or by the next Saturday night, but as

00:29:27.600 --> 00:29:30.870
you learn to develop your spirit

00:29:30.880 --> 00:29:33.750
and follow that inward witness, He will

00:29:33.760 --> 00:29:36.549
guide you in every area of your life.

00:29:38.159 --> 00:29:40.470
It won't come overnight,

00:29:40.480 --> 00:29:43.830
but as you develop it, be patient.

00:29:43.840 --> 00:29:46.070
I knew a man down in Texas who had never

00:29:46.080 --> 00:29:48.630
worn a pair of shoes until he was 12

00:29:48.640 --> 00:29:50.630
years old. He only had a

00:29:50.630 --> 00:29:50.640
fifth-grade

00:29:50.640 --> 00:29:52.630
education, but way back when money was

00:29:52.640 --> 00:29:54.789
money, he was a millionaire. Two

00:29:54.799 --> 00:29:56.789
different people—one from California

00:29:56.799 --> 00:29:58.549
and the other from Minnesota—who had

00:29:58.559 --> 00:30:00.230
been frequent houseguests in his home,

00:30:00.240 --> 00:30:02.230
told me that this man told

00:30:02.240 --> 00:30:04.630
each of them the same thing. He said to

00:30:04.640 --> 00:30:07.029
them both, 'In all these years and in

00:30:07.039 --> 00:30:08.870
all these investments—that's how

00:30:08.870 --> 00:30:08.880
he

00:30:08.880 --> 00:30:11.590
made his money—I never lost a

00:30:11.590 --> 00:30:11.600
dime.'That

00:30:11.600 --> 00:30:13.990
beats my record. How about yours?

00:30:14.000 --> 00:30:16.870
'Everything I have ever invested in

00:30:16.880 --> 00:30:18.870
has made money,'he said to each of them

00:30:18.880 --> 00:30:20.870
on different occasions. Then he told

00:30:20.880 --> 00:30:23.510
them how he did it: 'I always do this.

00:30:23.520 --> 00:30:25.430
When someone comes along with an idea

00:30:25.440 --> 00:30:27.510
wanting me to invest in

00:30:27.520 --> 00:30:30.310
something, my first reaction is mental.

00:30:30.320 --> 00:30:32.549
Now, I know what Jesus said: "When you

00:30:32.559 --> 00:30:35.029
pray, enter into your

00:30:35.029 --> 00:30:35.039
closet."He

00:30:35.039 --> 00:30:36.870
didn't necessarily mean you have to go

00:30:36.880 --> 00:30:39.110
get into a closet to pray. I know He

00:30:39.120 --> 00:30:41.909
meant for us to shut things out, but I

00:30:41.919 --> 00:30:43.830
have a large closet in my bedroom where

00:30:43.840 --> 00:30:46.630
I go to pray. I pray about it. I wait

00:30:46.640 --> 00:30:49.190
long enough until I hear what my spirit

00:30:49.200 --> 00:30:52.149
says. Sometimes I wait three days. Now,

00:30:52.159 --> 00:30:54.070
it doesn't mean that I stay in there 24

00:30:54.080 --> 00:30:56.549
hours a day. I might come out and eat

00:30:56.559 --> 00:31:01.590
one meal—usually, I miss a few. I

00:31:01.600 --> 00:31:03.510
come out and sleep a little bit, but the

00:31:03.520 --> 00:31:05.750
majority of the time I am waiting just

00:31:05.760 --> 00:31:08.470
by myself until I know by

00:31:08.480 --> 00:31:11.269
an inward witness what I am to do.

00:31:11.279 --> 00:31:13.430
Sometimes my head says, "Boy, you would

00:31:13.440 --> 00:31:15.269
be a fool to put your money in that;

00:31:15.279 --> 00:31:17.750
you'll lose your shirt."But my heart

00:31:17.760 --> 00:31:20.470
says, "Go ahead and invest in it."So I

00:31:20.480 --> 00:31:23.190
do. And in all these years, I have never

00:31:23.200 --> 00:31:26.230
lost a dime.'Then again, someone comes

00:31:26.240 --> 00:31:27.669
along with a deal and my head says,

00:31:27.679 --> 00:31:29.990
'Boy, you better get in on that

00:31:29.990 --> 00:31:30.000
one.'But

00:31:30.000 --> 00:31:32.070
I don't pay any attention to my

00:31:32.080 --> 00:31:35.430
head. I get in that closet and I wait.

00:31:35.440 --> 00:31:38.070
Sometimes all night long, I wait. I'll

00:31:38.080 --> 00:31:40.149
pray and read my Bible, but a lot of

00:31:40.149 --> 00:31:40.159
the

00:31:40.159 --> 00:31:43.350
time I just wait. I just get quiet until

00:31:43.360 --> 00:31:46.549
I hear inside what my heart says. When

00:31:46.559 --> 00:31:48.870
my heart says, 'No, don't do it,'and my

00:31:48.880 --> 00:31:50.870
head says, 'Yes, you better get in on

00:31:50.870 --> 00:31:50.880
it,'I

00:31:50.880 --> 00:31:53.830
don't do it. What had this man

00:31:53.840 --> 00:31:55.990
done? He had learned to follow the

00:31:56.000 --> 00:31:58.070
inward witness, and God had guided him

00:31:58.080 --> 00:32:00.630
in his business. By the late '30s and

00:32:00.640 --> 00:32:02.710
early '40s, he was already worth

00:32:02.710 --> 00:32:02.720
two

00:32:02.720 --> 00:32:05.430
million dollars. That doesn't sound big now,

00:32:05.440 --> 00:32:07.909
but it was then.

00:32:07.919 --> 00:32:09.750
Do you think God loved him more than He

00:32:09.760 --> 00:32:12.549
loves you? No. But this man took time to

00:32:12.559 --> 00:32:15.190
listen to God. He took steps and

00:32:15.200 --> 00:32:17.750
measures to wait upon God.

00:32:20.480 --> 00:32:24.070
The inward witness is

00:32:24.080 --> 00:32:26.230
just as supernatural as guidance through

00:32:26.240 --> 00:32:28.549
visions and so on; it is just not as

00:32:28.559 --> 00:32:31.509
spectacular. Many people are looking for

00:32:31.519 --> 00:32:33.909
the spectacular and they are missing the

00:32:33.919 --> 00:32:35.990
supernatural that is right there all the

00:32:36.000 --> 00:32:36.870
time.

00:32:36.880 --> 00:32:39.750
Yeah. Do you get it? That's what I'm

00:32:39.760 --> 00:32:41.909
trying to teach y'all. It's following

00:32:41.919 --> 00:32:44.389
that inward peace in your

00:32:44.389 --> 00:32:44.399
life—that

00:32:44.399 --> 00:32:45.990
peace that passes all

00:32:46.000 --> 00:32:47.990
understanding. There's so many times

00:32:48.000 --> 00:32:49.750
people come up to me and say, 'Hey, I

00:32:49.760 --> 00:32:52.789
believe this thing will help Megan.

00:32:52.799 --> 00:32:54.070
I believe because you know my daughter

00:32:54.080 --> 00:32:55.990
is overcoming

00:32:55.990 --> 00:32:56.000
autism.'They'll

00:32:56.000 --> 00:32:58.549
try to come up with some

00:32:58.559 --> 00:33:02.230
kind of health thing and tell us

00:33:02.240 --> 00:33:04.549
that this is the cure-all for

00:33:04.559 --> 00:33:06.870
her and you just put her on this or you

00:33:06.880 --> 00:33:09.350
put her on that, but my inward

00:33:09.350 --> 00:33:09.360
peace

00:33:09.360 --> 00:33:11.590
is not there. And I said,

00:33:11.600 --> 00:33:14.070
'I do not feel a green light on this.

00:33:14.080 --> 00:33:17.269
I feel this is like snake oil. This

00:33:17.279 --> 00:33:20.549
is not going to

00:33:20.549 --> 00:33:20.559
work.'But

00:33:20.559 --> 00:33:23.350
Brother Brandon, we've had all this

00:33:23.360 --> 00:33:25.269
research and all this stuff on it. And

00:33:25.279 --> 00:33:28.070
the Holy Spirit said, 'Don't

00:33:28.080 --> 00:33:30.389
do that. I'm telling you this is not for

00:33:30.389 --> 00:33:30.399
you.'And

00:33:30.399 --> 00:33:32.710
they say, 'Well, it's

00:33:32.720 --> 00:33:34.230
changed so many

00:33:34.230 --> 00:33:34.240
lives.'Well,

00:33:34.240 --> 00:33:35.909
good for them, but that's not for

00:33:35.919 --> 00:33:38.710
me. So, you have to go with the peace

00:33:38.720 --> 00:33:40.549
over your life. They could

00:33:40.559 --> 00:33:43.350
tell you that it's changed 50,000

00:33:43.360 --> 00:33:44.870
people's lives and they're better and

00:33:44.880 --> 00:33:46.470
everything else has done it and it's the

00:33:46.470 --> 00:33:46.480
cure-all

00:33:46.480 --> 00:33:48.710
for them. But if you don't have

00:33:48.720 --> 00:33:51.350
a peace for you, then you follow that

00:33:51.360 --> 00:33:53.509
inward peace and you pray. It's like

00:33:53.519 --> 00:33:55.509
he went into his closet for

00:33:55.519 --> 00:33:57.269
two or three days sometimes

00:33:57.279 --> 00:33:59.269
and would go in there and pray and seek the

00:33:59.279 --> 00:34:01.350
Lord for himself.

00:34:01.360 --> 00:34:03.830
Everybody is different. Nobody's

00:34:03.830 --> 00:34:03.840
cookie-cutter.

00:34:03.840 --> 00:34:05.909
God did not make

00:34:05.909 --> 00:34:05.919
cookie-cutter

00:34:05.919 --> 00:34:08.149
Christians and pull them out and cook

00:34:08.159 --> 00:34:09.349
them on a sheet and say, 'Look,

00:34:09.359 --> 00:34:11.589
everybody looks like a

00:34:11.589 --> 00:34:11.599
gingerbread.'Everyone

00:34:11.599 --> 00:34:13.190
looks

00:34:13.200 --> 00:34:14.790
different, but

00:34:14.800 --> 00:34:15.750
we're all different.

00:34:15.760 --> 00:34:16.149
Yeah.

00:34:16.159 --> 00:34:17.909
But we're all made in His image and we

00:34:17.919 --> 00:34:19.349
all have the Holy Spirit on the inside

00:34:19.359 --> 00:34:21.349
of us if you're a born-again Christian.

00:34:21.359 --> 00:34:23.349
I believe with all my heart

00:34:23.359 --> 00:34:25.270
He'll guide each and every single one of

00:34:25.280 --> 00:34:26.869
us. But it's going to be different. So

00:34:26.879 --> 00:34:28.950
you can't get disappointed if He tells

00:34:28.960 --> 00:34:31.589
you no and you feel like Billy Bob over

00:34:31.599 --> 00:34:33.829
here was told yes. Why'd He tell you no?

00:34:33.839 --> 00:34:35.990
I don't know. Just follow the peace of

00:34:36.000 --> 00:34:38.710
God for you and whatever you feel in

00:34:38.720 --> 00:34:40.310
your heart, do it with all your heart,

00:34:40.320 --> 00:34:41.669
mind, soul, and strength. I had one lady

00:34:41.679 --> 00:34:43.829
say, 'I hear all these people talking

00:34:43.839 --> 00:34:46.149
about investing in gold and silver, but

00:34:46.159 --> 00:34:48.149
the Lord told me not to do it. What do

00:34:48.159 --> 00:34:49.990
you think that's about? Should I do

00:34:49.990 --> 00:34:50.000
it?'I

00:34:50.000 --> 00:34:52.470
said, 'No, if the Holy Spirit told you

00:34:52.480 --> 00:34:54.629
not to do it, then don't do it.'I can't

00:34:54.639 --> 00:34:57.270
answer for you. I just know that that's

00:34:57.280 --> 00:34:59.190
what the Holy Spirit has told certain

00:34:59.200 --> 00:35:00.150
people

00:35:00.160 --> 00:35:02.790
and they may say, 'Hey, I took hundreds

00:35:02.800 --> 00:35:05.349
of thousands of dollars and invested in gold and

00:35:05.359 --> 00:35:07.589
silver,'and

00:35:07.599 --> 00:35:09.510
then the

00:35:09.520 --> 00:35:11.910
Lord said, 'Don't do that for

00:35:11.910 --> 00:35:11.920
you.'I

00:35:11.920 --> 00:35:13.589
can't question that. You have to follow

00:35:13.599 --> 00:35:14.390
your peace.

00:35:15.599 --> 00:35:17.589
I think that's the best. You will

00:35:17.599 --> 00:35:20.550
never ever miss it if you follow the

00:35:20.560 --> 00:35:21.670
peace.

00:35:21.680 --> 00:35:23.589
This is one thing: we tried to fleece

00:35:23.599 --> 00:35:25.109
God once, and a lot of people try to

00:35:25.119 --> 00:35:26.630
fleece God. They say, you know, like

00:35:26.640 --> 00:35:29.109
Gideon, Gideon put the fleece out there

00:35:29.119 --> 00:35:32.790
and did all that he did and the

00:35:32.800 --> 00:35:36.150
Lord used it to help him. But

00:35:36.160 --> 00:35:37.670
Gideon didn't have the Holy Spirit

00:35:37.680 --> 00:35:39.510
dwelling on the inside of him like we

00:35:39.520 --> 00:35:39.990
have.

00:35:40.880 --> 00:35:41.670
That was Old Covenant.

00:35:42.240 --> 00:35:42.790
And so,

00:35:42.800 --> 00:35:43.829
under the New Covenant now,

00:35:43.839 --> 00:35:45.510
you can put out a fleece and

00:35:45.520 --> 00:35:48.390
get fleeced real quick.

00:35:48.400 --> 00:35:50.790
But I've done it, and

00:35:50.800 --> 00:35:52.390
I'm not recommending anybody else

00:35:52.400 --> 00:35:53.910
do it, but I did it. I told

00:35:53.920 --> 00:35:55.910
the Lord whenever we were starting

00:35:55.920 --> 00:35:58.150
out to go full-time doing eBay

00:35:58.160 --> 00:36:01.589
and Poshmark, and then

00:36:01.599 --> 00:36:04.069
I felt the Holy Spirit say, 'I want you

00:36:04.079 --> 00:36:06.390
to tell Diana it's time for

00:36:06.400 --> 00:36:09.030
her to move on from the church doing

00:36:09.040 --> 00:36:10.230
accounting there

00:36:10.240 --> 00:36:13.190
and I want you to go full-time into

00:36:13.190 --> 00:36:13.200
this.'And

00:36:13.200 --> 00:36:15.030
I thought, 'Oh

00:36:15.030 --> 00:36:15.040
man.'I

00:36:15.040 --> 00:36:17.910
never told her at all. I was

00:36:17.920 --> 00:36:19.510
scared actually because I said,

00:36:19.520 --> 00:36:22.470
'Man, I like the security of

00:36:22.480 --> 00:36:24.150
every two weeks having

00:36:24.150 --> 00:36:24.160
something.'The

00:36:24.160 --> 00:36:26.069
Lord said, 'Brandon, you're asking me

00:36:26.079 --> 00:36:28.630
for increase and I'm trying to bring

00:36:28.640 --> 00:36:30.870
increase to you. You've got to

00:36:30.880 --> 00:36:33.750
let go.'It's like an acrobat.

00:36:35.680 --> 00:36:38.150
A trapeze artist grabs on to the

00:36:38.160 --> 00:36:40.150
next thing, but you don't want to let go

00:36:40.160 --> 00:36:41.910
of what's behind you because it's

00:36:41.920 --> 00:36:44.550
comfortable. You've got to sometimes let

00:36:44.560 --> 00:36:46.950
go and grab on by faith to the next

00:36:46.960 --> 00:36:49.510
thing so that God can take you from glory

00:36:49.520 --> 00:36:51.990
to glory. But many times we

00:36:52.000 --> 00:36:54.790
latch on to what's behind us and we don't want

00:36:54.800 --> 00:36:56.630
to let go of it. But God's saying go out

00:36:56.640 --> 00:36:58.310
and grab on to the next thing.

00:36:58.320 --> 00:36:59.910
You're going to have to do some things

00:36:59.920 --> 00:37:02.550
by faith. And it may make your

00:37:02.560 --> 00:37:05.109
flesh feel uncomfortable to do what

00:37:05.119 --> 00:37:07.270
I've asked you to do. But you've got to

00:37:07.280 --> 00:37:09.109
be obedient.

00:37:09.119 --> 00:37:10.790
And sometimes you're just going to

00:37:10.800 --> 00:37:13.109
have to do it blindly. Just do what He

00:37:13.119 --> 00:37:14.710
tells you to do and do it by faith. If

00:37:14.720 --> 00:37:16.470
He says do it, well, I don't see how it

00:37:16.470 --> 00:37:16.480
makes

00:37:16.480 --> 00:37:18.470
any sense,

00:37:18.480 --> 00:37:19.910
and you grab on to it and you

00:37:19.910 --> 00:37:19.920
swing

00:37:19.920 --> 00:37:21.349
out and you're in a better

00:37:21.359 --> 00:37:23.190
position than what you were because you

00:37:23.200 --> 00:37:24.710
stepped out by faith. And

00:37:24.720 --> 00:37:26.870
that's where

00:37:26.880 --> 00:37:30.230
we were. I

00:37:30.240 --> 00:37:31.670
didn't want to step out. She didn't know

00:37:31.680 --> 00:37:33.670
the Lord was dealing with me this way. But

00:37:33.680 --> 00:37:35.750
I told Him, I said, 'Lord, if this is

00:37:35.760 --> 00:37:38.950
you, then let there be four inches of

00:37:38.950 --> 00:37:38.960
rain,'because

00:37:38.960 --> 00:37:41.109
I know in Oklahoma in the

00:37:41.119 --> 00:37:43.190
middle of summer, we don't get a lot of

00:37:43.200 --> 00:37:46.150
rain. It's dry a lot of times.

00:37:46.160 --> 00:37:48.390
So I was trying to make it really

00:37:48.400 --> 00:37:50.390
hard.

00:37:50.400 --> 00:37:52.710
I thought, 'Lord, I'm going to

00:37:52.720 --> 00:37:54.150
make this one

00:37:54.160 --> 00:37:56.310
unmistakable.'And

00:37:56.320 --> 00:37:59.030
I told Him, I said, 'If you

00:37:59.040 --> 00:38:03.270
make it four inches of rain in one night, I'll

00:38:03.280 --> 00:38:05.270
know it's you and we'll quit

00:38:05.280 --> 00:38:06.790
and I'll move by faith. But

00:38:06.800 --> 00:38:08.790
right now, Father, I'm tired. I

00:38:08.800 --> 00:38:11.010
need you to give me a

00:38:11.020 --> 00:38:14.310
sign.'On

00:38:14.320 --> 00:38:18.310
July the 5th,

00:38:18.320 --> 00:38:21.670
it rained four inches—not just in one night,

00:38:21.670 --> 00:38:21.680
but

00:38:21.680 --> 00:38:26.310
in about an hour or two-hour span.

00:38:26.320 --> 00:38:28.870
It came down and the storm parked right

00:38:28.880 --> 00:38:31.430
over the top of the house.

00:38:31.440 --> 00:38:33.589
It was a toad strangler.

00:38:33.599 --> 00:38:35.990
I'm talking cow patty lifting going down

00:38:36.000 --> 00:38:38.870
the road. I'm talking more rain than was

00:38:38.880 --> 00:38:41.109
standing and it was a gully washer. I

00:38:41.109 --> 00:38:41.119
stood

00:38:41.119 --> 00:38:43.190
up there and I thought, 'Are

00:38:43.200 --> 00:38:44.870
we going to see that four inches of rain?

00:38:44.880 --> 00:38:46.870
Even if it's three and a half,

00:38:46.880 --> 00:38:49.510
it's not what I asked

00:38:49.520 --> 00:38:53.190
for,'because

00:38:53.200 --> 00:38:54.870
I didn't want to do it.

00:38:54.880 --> 00:38:56.630
Forgive me, Lord. You know my

00:38:56.640 --> 00:38:58.150
heart.

00:38:58.160 --> 00:39:00.390
But it got up to four inches. I went

00:39:00.400 --> 00:39:01.589
out there and checked the thing and

00:39:07.359 --> 00:39:11.109
it was

00:39:11.119 --> 00:39:12.790
four inches.

00:39:12.800 --> 00:39:14.630
Right on.

00:39:14.640 --> 00:39:16.870
I started screaming and I went, 'Praise

00:39:16.880 --> 00:39:19.190
God. Okay, God, we'll do

00:39:19.190 --> 00:39:19.200
it.'I

00:39:19.200 --> 00:39:21.510
put

00:39:21.520 --> 00:39:24.150
the food coloring inside of it

00:39:24.160 --> 00:39:26.230
so I could take a picture of it

00:39:26.240 --> 00:39:28.950
as a reminder of what

00:39:28.960 --> 00:39:31.910
God did for us to show me to step out by

00:39:31.920 --> 00:39:34.470
faith. And right

00:39:34.480 --> 00:39:37.270
after Labor Day, you walked in and

00:39:37.280 --> 00:39:39.109
you did what the Lord told us to do and

00:39:39.119 --> 00:39:41.030
we've never looked back since.

00:39:41.040 --> 00:39:43.910
God has provided and taken care of us.

00:39:43.920 --> 00:39:47.109
We thought, 'Why did we wait

00:39:47.119 --> 00:39:49.430
so long out of fear of letting go of the

00:39:49.440 --> 00:39:51.270
baton of

00:39:51.270 --> 00:39:51.280
the acrobat?'We

00:39:51.280 --> 00:39:52.790
don't recommend the fleecing.

00:39:52.800 --> 00:39:54.790
But

00:39:54.800 --> 00:39:57.829
I was struggling

00:39:57.839 --> 00:40:00.069
and He came through where I needed Him.

00:40:00.079 --> 00:40:02.870
I'm so thankful for Him.

00:40:02.880 --> 00:40:04.710
Sometimes when you're

00:40:04.720 --> 00:40:07.510
weak, He makes

00:40:07.520 --> 00:40:10.310
you strong. And even in those times,

00:40:10.320 --> 00:40:12.710
it was

00:40:12.720 --> 00:40:15.190
mercy that brought me through.

00:40:16.720 --> 00:40:19.270
It was God's grace when we needed it the

00:40:19.280 --> 00:40:20.470
most.

00:40:20.480 --> 00:40:22.630
But we let go

00:40:22.640 --> 00:40:24.630
of that and we just reached out and we

00:40:24.640 --> 00:40:26.550
grabbed on to it and, like I said,

00:40:26.560 --> 00:40:27.910
never looked back since.

00:40:27.920 --> 00:40:29.349
And if you told me to do it in the

00:40:29.359 --> 00:40:30.950
natural, my flesh was screaming

00:40:31.680 --> 00:40:33.670
because I just got laid off because our

00:40:33.680 --> 00:40:36.790
pastor fell morally not too long

00:40:36.800 --> 00:40:37.430
from then.

00:40:37.440 --> 00:40:39.430
They had to lay off a lot of employees.

00:40:42.240 --> 00:40:44.150
The finances dried up.

00:40:44.800 --> 00:40:48.390
But you know what? God's always

00:40:48.400 --> 00:40:51.990
faithful. Even in my stubbornness when

00:40:51.990 --> 00:40:52.000
He was

00:40:52.000 --> 00:40:53.670
trying to tell me to do something, He

00:40:53.680 --> 00:40:56.710
was still merciful. There

00:40:56.710 --> 00:40:56.720
are

00:40:56.720 --> 00:40:58.870
some more stories, but

00:40:58.880 --> 00:41:00.710
for the sake of time, we won't

00:41:00.720 --> 00:41:03.430
get into those today.

00:41:03.440 --> 00:41:05.270
I just wanted to come on and

00:41:05.280 --> 00:41:09.430
encourage you all to live by faith. Live

00:41:09.440 --> 00:41:11.910
with everything you have inside of you:

00:41:11.920 --> 00:41:13.910
the Holy Spirit. Faith comes by

00:41:13.920 --> 00:41:15.750
hearing, and hearing by the word of God.

00:41:15.760 --> 00:41:18.390
Encourage yourself today by getting in

00:41:18.400 --> 00:41:22.710
the Word. Pray and pray some more.

00:41:22.720 --> 00:41:24.470
The Lord said to me, "Brandon, I want you

00:41:24.480 --> 00:41:28.470
to be quick to pray and slow to

00:41:28.480 --> 00:41:32.550
speak, quick to get in My Word and slow

00:41:32.560 --> 00:41:35.190
to make decisions. Don't do things

00:41:35.190 --> 00:41:35.200
hastily;

00:41:35.200 --> 00:41:39.510
do not be hasty in anything.

00:41:39.520 --> 00:41:41.190
I'm not in a hurry; the Holy Spirit's

00:41:41.200 --> 00:41:42.790
not in a

00:41:42.790 --> 00:41:42.800
hurry."Follow

00:41:42.800 --> 00:41:44.470
the peace that passes all

00:41:44.480 --> 00:41:46.150
understanding in your life.

00:41:46.160 --> 00:41:48.150
As we pray for this

00:41:48.160 --> 00:41:50.309
country, for our

00:41:50.319 --> 00:41:52.470
government, the finances, and

00:41:52.480 --> 00:41:54.230
all the things that we have,

00:41:55.760 --> 00:41:58.950
don't take the care of it. Do not take

00:41:58.960 --> 00:42:02.470
the care of the election for 2024

00:42:02.480 --> 00:42:06.470
and say, "Well, if so-and-so wins

00:42:06.480 --> 00:42:09.190
the election, our country is done

00:42:09.190 --> 00:42:09.200
for."No,

00:42:09.200 --> 00:42:12.550
I don't believe that with all my

00:42:12.560 --> 00:42:15.670
heart. I believe that God

00:42:15.680 --> 00:42:18.069
is going to—we're going to have a

00:42:18.079 --> 00:42:20.150
major revival yet, and there's going to

00:42:20.160 --> 00:42:21.990
be a major outpouring of the Spirit of

00:42:22.000 --> 00:42:24.069
the Lord on this generation like we've

00:42:24.079 --> 00:42:26.470
never seen before. Part of what He told

00:42:26.470 --> 00:42:26.480
me—and

00:42:26.480 --> 00:42:28.790
I did not say this last

